headline: Latest News In AI Chips - Revolutionizing AI Factory Power with Digital Twin Technology
summary: Schneider Electric and ETAP have launched the world’s first digital twin specifically designed to simulate the power requirements of AI factories from the grid to the chip level, utilizing NVIDIA Omniverse technology. This innovative solution allows for advanced insight and control over AI Factory electrical systems, with potential benefits including enhanced energy efficiency, predictive maintenance, and reductions in total cost of ownership.
